properties.SQL Query:
SELECT
    county_name,
    county_uuid,
    county_focal_person_uuid,
    sub_county_name AS branch_name,
    sub_county_uuid AS subcounty_uuid,
    sub_county_focal_person_uuid,
    chu_uuid,
    chu_code,
    chu_code AS mcul_code,
    chu_name,
    chu_name AS community_unit,
    cha_uuid,
    facility_join_field,
    
    period_start,
    period,
    period_start_epoch,
    number_of_chps,
    number_of_chps AS count_chws,
    
    count_households AS families_registered_all_time,
    count_households_visited_new_visit AS families_registered,
    count_households_visited_revisit AS count_households_with_home_visit,
    
    count_new_households_visited_safe_water_new_visit AS households_using_treated_water,
    count_households_hand_washing_facilities_new_visit AS households_with_hand_washing_facilities,
    count_households_functional_latrines_new_visit AS households_with_functional_latrines,
    count_households_new_visit_refuse_disposal AS households_with_refuse_disposal_facilities,
    
    count_households_new_visit_upto_date_insurance AS count_households_with_updated_insurance,
    count_households_new_visit_upto_date_insurance_uhc AS count_households_with_updated_insurance_uhc,
    count_households_new_visit_upto_date_insurance_nhif AS count_households_with_updated_insurance_nhif,
    count_households_new_visit_upto_date_insurance_others AS count_households_with_updated_insurance_other,
    
    count_women_pregnant AS pregnancies_registered,
    count_women_pregnant_underage AS underage_pregnancies,
    count_women_pregnant_counselled_anc AS count_pregnant_women_counselled_for_anc_services,
    count_pregnant_women_referred_to_health_facility AS count_pregnant_women_referred_to_hf,
    count_women_pregnant_referred_anc_completed AS count_pregnancy_referrals_reaching_hf,
    
    count_new_deliveries AS total_deliveries,
    count_new_deliveries_at_health_facility AS total_deliveries_at_hf,
    count_new_deliveries_at_home AS total_deliveries_at_home,
    count_new_deliveries_underage AS total_underage_deliveries_10_19_yrs,
    count_new_mothers_visited_within_48_hours_of_delivery AS count_newborn_visited_at_home_within_48_hrs,
    count_new_deliveries_at_home_referred_pnc AS count_home_deliveries_referred_for_pnc_services,
    count_women_referred_pnc_completed AS count_pnc_referrals_reaching_hf,
    
    count_women_15_49_years_counselled_fp AS count_women_15_49_yrs_counselled_fp_methods,
    count_women_15_49_years_provided_fp AS count_women_15_49_yrs_provided_fp_commodities,
    count_women_15_49_years_referred_fp AS count_women_15_49_yrs_referred_fp_services,
    count_women_15_49_years_referred_fp_completed AS count_fp_services_referral_reaching_hf,
    
    count_newborns_within_48_hours_of_delivery AS count_new_mothers_visited_within_48_hrs,
    count_children_12_59_months_dewormed,
    count_children_0_11_months_referred_immunization AS count_children_0_11_months_referred_for_immunization,
    count_children_6_59_months_referred_vitamin_a,
    count_children_0_59_months_referred_delayed_milestones AS count_children_with_delayed_dev_milestone_referred,
    
    count_children_6_59_months_malnutrition_severe AS count_children_6_59_months_with_red_muac,
    count_children_6_59_months_malnutrition_moderate AS count_children_6_59_months_with_yellow_muac,
    
    count_cases_0_59_months_fever_lt_7_days AS count_fever_cases_u5,
    count_cases_0_59_months_fever_lt_7_days_rdt AS count_fever_cases_mrdt_7days_u5,
    count_cases_0_59_months_fever_lt_7_days_rdt_positive AS count_fever_cases_mrdt_positive_7days_u5,
    count_cases_0_59_months_fever_lt_7_days_rdt_positive_act AS count_malaria_u5_given_act,
    count_cases_2_59_months_fast_breathing AS count_fast_breathing_2mo_59mo,
    count_cases_2_59_months_fast_breathing_amoxycillin AS count_gave_amox_2mo_59mo,
    count_cases_2_59_months_diarrhea AS count_diarrhoea_cases_2mo_59mo,
    count_cases_2_59_months_diarrhea_zinc_ors AS diarrhoea_2mo_59mo_ors_zinc,
    
    count_cases_gte_60_months_fever_lt_7_days AS count_fever_cases_o5,
    count_cases_gte_60_months_fever_lt_7_days_rdt AS count_fever_cases_mrdt_7days_o5,
    count_cases_gte_60_months_fever_lt_7_days_rdt_positive AS count_fever_cases_mrdt_positive_7days_o5,
    count_cases_gte_60_months_fever_lt_7_days_rdt_positive_act AS count_malaria_o5_given_act,
    
    count_persons_screened_tb AS count_persons_screened_for_tb,
    count_persons_presumptive_tb_referred AS count_presumptive_tb_persons_referred_for_tb_diagnosis,
    count_persons_presumptive_tb_referred_confirmed AS count_presumptive_tb_contacts_referred_for_screening,
    count_persons_presumptive_tb_referred_confirmed_referred AS count_confirmed_tb_cases_from_clinic,
    count_cases_tb_confirmed_0_59_months AS count_children_u5_yrs_tb_contacts_referred_for_ipt,
    count_treatment_interruptors_tb AS count_tb_treatment_interrupters,
    count_treatment_interrupters_tb_traced AS count_count_tb_treatment_interrupters_traced,
    count_persons_presumptive_tb_referred_completed AS count_presumptive_tb_cases_referrals_reaching_hf,
    count_persons_presumptive_tb_contacts_referred_completed AS count_presumptive_tb_contacts_referrals_reaching_hf,
    count_cases_tb_0_59_months_ipt_referred_completed AS count_u5_child_tb_contacts_for_ipt_reaching_hf,
    count_treatment_interruptors_tb_referred_completed AS count_tb_interrupters_referrals_reaching_hf,
    
    count_defaulters_immunization_referred AS count_immunization_defaulters,
    count_defaulters_immunization_referred_completed AS count_immunization_referrals_reaching_hf,
    count_defaulters_art_referred AS count_art_defaulters,
    count_defaulters_art_traced_referred AS count_art_defaulters_traced_referred,
    count_defaulters_art_referred_completed AS count_art_referrals_reaching_hf,
    count_defaulters_hei_referred AS count_hiv_exposed_infant_defaulters,
    count_defaulters_hei_traced_referred AS count_hiv_exposed_infant_defaulters_traced_referred,
    count_defaulters_hei_referred_completed AS count_hei_referrals_reaching_hf,
    
    count_persons_referred_hts AS count_referred_hiv_testing_services_hts,
    count_persons_referred_hts_completed AS count_hts_referrals_reaching_hf,
    count_persons_referred_comprehensive_geriatric_services AS count_persons_60_plus_yrs_referred_for_cgs_checkups,
    count_persons_referred_diabetes AS count_known_cases_diabetes,
    count_persons_referred_cancer AS count_known_cases_cancer,
    count_persons_referred_mental_illness AS count_known_cases_mental_illness,
    count_persons_referred_hypertension AS count_known_cases_hypertension,
    count_routine_checkup_referred_completed AS count_routine_checkups_referrals_reaching_hf,
    
    count_deaths_0_28_days AS count_infant_deaths_0_28_days,
    count_deaths_29_days_11_months AS count_infant_deaths_29_days_11_months,
    count_deaths_12_59_months AS count_infant_deaths_12_59_months,
    count_deaths_maternal AS count_maternal_deaths,
    count_deaths_6_59_years,
    count_deaths_gt_60_years AS count_deaths_60_above_years,
	0 AS count_community_dialogue_days_held,
    0 AS count_community_action_days_held,
    0 AS count_cu_monthly_meetings_held
FROM v1.khis_summary_data_last_month
INSERT INTO public.moh_515_khis_reports(doc_uuid, chew_uuid, mcul_code, year, month) values ('${doc_uuid}', '${chew_uuid}', '${mcul_code}', '${year}', '${month}');

SELECT COUNT (*) FROM public.moh_515_khis_reports
where doc_uuid='${doc_uuid}' and chew_uuid='${chew_uuid}' 
and mcul_code='${mcul_code}'

UPDATE moh_515_khis_reports SET date_submitted = '${now():format('YYYY-MM-dd HH:mm:ss')}', status = 'success'
WHERE doc_uuid = '${doc_uuid}' AND chew_uuid = '${chew_uuid}' AND mcul_code = '${mcul_code}'

UPDATE moh_515_khis_reports SET date_submitted = '${now():format('YYYY-MM-dd HH:mm:ss')}', status = 'failed'
WHERE doc_uuid = '${doc_uuid}' AND chew_uuid = '${chew_uuid}' AND mcul_code = '${mcul_code}'
